      • put

        public MapBuilder<K,V> put(@Nullable
                  K key,
                  @NotNull
                  Builder<V> value)
        Put a value in the builder's map, represented by a Builder of that value.

        Note that the given Builder is not invoked to build the value right away, it is invoked once for each call to Builder.get().

        Parameters:
        key - The key at which to put the value.
        value - The value to put at the given key.
        Returns:
        This builder instance itself, for chaining convenience.
